data.description: ***VIRTUAL 3D TOUR ON LINK 1*** 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom two-story home nestled in the Sawgrass Bay Community. Step inside to discover an open great room floor plan, offering a warm and welcoming space for you and your loved ones. The soft, neutral colors throughout create a cozy and inviting atmosphere. This beauty, built in 2019, features upgraded ceilings. The kitchen is a true delight with plenty of counter space, including a convenient one-level island, and it comes equipped with stainless steel appliances. Natural light pours in through the sliding glass doors, offering a lovely view of the backyard. The master suite is your personal retreat, providing a scenic view of the extra-large lot. The master bath boasts raised vanities, dual sinks, and a generously sized tub.The first floor also includes a builder-upgraded bedroom and bathroom. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious loft area, three more roomy bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a convenient laundry room.  The Sawgrass Bay Community is a wonderful place to live, featuring playgrounds, recreation areas, and a welcoming community pool. You'll love the incredible location, just a stone's throw from Clermont's shopping, dining, and services. Plus, it's a breeze to get to Disney and other attractions. With downtown Orlando a mere 40 minutes away and the Orlando International Airport just 45 minutes away, you can't ask for a better spot. Hurry and make an appointment to see this beauty today because inventory is limited, and this home won't last long.
